    <bioghist encodinganalog="545$a">
      <head>Historical Information
</head>
      <p>Louisa was formed in 1742 from Hanover County.      
</p>
      <p>The will books of Louisa in this collection were created by the County Court.
</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Will Books, 1746-1902, of Louisa County Court. The will book includes the name of testator, list of heirs and the year the wills were proven in court and probate records such as inventories and appraisements.  The will books have indexes which contains the first and last names of both parties.  It is arranged alphabetically from A-Z.  Will Book (1757-1902) is not fully proven.  
</p>
    </scopecontent>
